    "description": "<p>Magenta Cyan Consultancy is a Social Media &amp; Project Management Consultancy based in sunny Singapore in South East Asia.</p>\n<p>We are a one stop shop to promoting your business in the Social Media world of Facebook &amp; Instagram!</p>\n<p>We provide businesses with a way to engage with existing customers and reach new ones while allowing them to promote their desired culture, mission, or tone.</p>\n<p>We can help manage and alleviate the day to day admin of Social Media Management by taking on that task for you, so that you can focus on other areas of your business.</p>\n<p>We have helped many clients reach global audiences far and wide, therefore gaining traction and in return sales!</p>",
